headline: 3 Reasons WYNN is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: The past six months have been a windfall for Wynn Resorts’s shareholders. The company’s stock price has jumped 42.5%, hitting $126.71 per share. This run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
